Key Match Events: Six different scorers finished in double figures for the Pistons
Wendell Moore Jr. and Marcus Sasser made key contributions in the fourth quarter
Ron Holland II finished with ten points, eight rebounds, and three steals
Malik Beasley led the Pistons in scoring with 20 points
Cade Cunningham recorded his sixth double-double of the season
Post-Match Reflections: Cunningham praised the contributions of Moore Jr. and Sasser
Cunningham expressed happiness for Ron Holland II's performance
Cunningham highlighted Holland II's mental strength
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Pistons defeated the Toronto Raptors 99-95
Tim Hardaway Jr. and Simone Fontecchio were unavailable due to injuries
Jaden Ivey returned from injury and contributed 14 points
